$interpreted: : The Kingdom of the Sun's civil war has come to a standstill. Sharice Carterwell, too late to follow her childhood dreams, has come face to face with fate once again, a chance encounter with a myserious being. And thus, a brand new adventure begins...

Sharice: It's been raining for days...
I wonder how they're all doing.
Sharice: Hey, Hestia~ Stupid bird~ Big ugly rat~
Sharice: No one's here? Oh come on, I came all the way here...
Sharice: Birdbrain?
Sharice: Hmph, well whatever, I'm not here to see you guys anyway! I just didn't feel like going home, and I was in the neighborhood...
Sharice: Ugh, whatever! Just pretend I'm not here, that's cool...
Sharice: What, got rocks in your ears?
Sharice: !!!
Sharice: Puggi, what's wrong with you? Something's growing out of your head!!

Puggi: This shorty looks so familiar... 
Who are you?
Sharice: Who am I!? C'mon birdbrain, is this a prank or something?
Puggi: Birdbrain... am I a birdbrain?

Puggi: I just have way too many fans~
I'm sorry if I can't remember who they all are.
Puggi: But... where am I, anywhere? Where are we?
Sharice: You don't know where this is??

Puggi: I just remember finding something in the mountains... 
I was so hungry... so thirsty...
Puggi: Next thing I remember... I was here?
Sharice: (Does he have amnesia or something? What's that thing sprouting from his head?)
Puggi: Owww—let go of me!!
Puggi: Agh...! You trying to kill me or something!?
Sharice: What the...!? Why won't it come out!?
Puggi: Who? Who's that calling me?
Sharice: Wait... where are you going?
Sharice: Just wait here with me until that rat gets back here.
Puggi: ...But someone's calling my name... Don't you hear it?
Sharice: I... I don't hear anything!
Sharice: I swear you better not be pranking me!
???: <color=#227700>Child... Child...</color>
Puggi: I hear that voice again...
Sharice: Wahh, hey!! Don't run!

Sharice: Whew... Where am I?
I've never been this far in the forest before...
Sharice: (I've got to stick close to Puggi...)
Puggi: It's close... so close...
Sharice: Where the heck are you going!?
Sharice: There's not even a road here! You better not get us lost!
Puggi: But that voice... keeps calling me...
Puggi: I have to follow it...
Sharice: Oh come on, there's no voi... huh?
Weak Voice: Oola... Oooo... Dora...
Sharice: What was that!?
Puggi: Sounds like someone crying. I think it's coming from over there?
Sharice: Was that the voice you're talking about?
Puggi: No... The voice I heard was much older.
Weak Voice: ...Ooolllaa... Oodoraaa...
Puggi: Not this annoying crying kid~
Sharice: You... you think someone's in trouble?
Weak Voice: Oooo... Ooollaaa...
Sharice: I think it's coming from here.
Puggi: Why do I feel like... this place is a little bit familiar?
Sharice: Familiar? Do you remember something?
Puggi: I don't know... let's check it out.
Sharice: B... But...
Sharice: Ah! This is ridiculous!!
Sharice: Ugh... this cave is way too dark. Wahh!!
Sharice: Hey birdbrain, watch where you're touching!
Puggi: Oh, was that you? I thought it was the wall...
Sharice: ......
Puggi: Oh!? There's some light ahead!
Puggi: Must be the exit!
